// SnippetEditor
// Editor for code snippets stored in a JSON envelope.
// Displays syntax-highlighted code with optional diff view, annotation support,
// and an "Apply" action that sends the snippet to the file system via the API.

Snippet content is a JSON envelope: {code, language, filePath, originalCode,
highlightLines, annotations, groupId}. The editor parses this on load and
re-serializes on save, preserving all non-code fields.

FUNCTION detectLanguage(fileName) -> Language                          EXPORT
  Maps file extension (ts, tsx, py, rs, go, etc.) to Language enum values.

---

FUNCTION parseSnippetData(rawContent) -> SnippetData                  EXPORT
  Attempts JSON.parse on rawContent. Extracts code, language, filePath,
  originalCode, highlightLines, annotations. Falls back gracefully if not JSON.

---

FUNCTION serializeSnippetData(newCode, rawContent) -> string           EXPORT
  Re-encodes the JSON envelope with updated code and current annotations,
  preserving all other fields from the original envelope.

---

FUNCTION SnippetEditor(snippet, onChange, onSave, onToolbarControls, ...) -> JSX  EXPORT
  CALLS: CodeMirrorWrapper (CodeMirrorWrapper)
  Parses snippet content via parseSnippetData on load.
  Pushes memoized toolbarControls JSX to parent via onToolbarControls in effect.
  Renders CodeMirrorWrapper with annotation support.
  Renders annotation popover when a dot is clicked.

---

FUNCTION handleContentChange(newContent) -> void
  Updates content state, calls onChange.

---

FUNCTION handleLanguageChange(lang) -> void
  Updates selectedLanguage state.

---

FUNCTION handleDiffToggle() -> void
  Toggles showDiff.

---

FUNCTION handleCopy() -> void
  Copies current code to clipboard. Flashes button text to "Copied!" for 1.5s.

---

FUNCTION handleSave() -> void
  Serializes content via serializeSnippetData. Calls updateSnippet.
  Updates originalCode ref. Calls onSave.

---

FUNCTION handleApply() -> void
  Saves first (calls handleSave), then calls api.applySnippet(snippet.id).
  Shows apply status message for 3s.

---

FUNCTION handleCancel() -> void
  Resets content to originalCode. Hides diff.

---

FUNCTION saveAnnotations(newAnnotations) -> void
  Updates annotations state and persists via updateSnippet.

---

FUNCTION handleAnnotationClick(index) -> void
  Opens edit popover for the clicked annotation index.

---

FUNCTION handleOpenAddAnnotation() -> void
  Creates a new annotation from currentSelection. Calls saveAnnotations.

---

FUNCTION handleAnnotationSave(annotation) -> void
  Saves new or updated annotation from the popover via saveAnnotations.

---

FUNCTION handleAnnotationDelete(index) -> void
  Removes annotation at index via saveAnnotations.

---

FUNCTION handleInlineAnnotationSave(index, annotation) -> void
  Direct save from CodeMirror inline widget without opening popover.

---

FUNCTION handleInlineAnnotationDelete(index) -> void
  Direct delete from CodeMirror inline widget.

---

FUNCTION handleClearAnnotations() -> void
  Clears all annotations via saveAnnotations([]).
